了起来。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="马铃薯实验室|官方预告片| Netflix [Eng Sub]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/abDfjHG78vY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2>如何观看<em>土豆实验室</em>？ </h2><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_tags tdi_87 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2" data-td-block-uid="tdi_87"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><em>马铃薯实验室</em>将于3月1日通过韩国有线网络TVN首播，此后每个星期六和周日下午9:20 PM KST播出新剧集。该系列将同时在Netflix上为国际观众流式传输。</div></div><p>该邮报<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-potato-lab-netflix-k-drama-trailer-cast-plot-more-kang-tae-oh-lee-sun-bin-3838857">观看Netflix K-Drama“马铃薯实验室”的预告片，由Kang Tae-Oh和Lee Sun-bin主演，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
