="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez-benny-blanco@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez-benny-blanco@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez-benny-blanco@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez-benny-blanco@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez-benny-blanco@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/selena-gomez-benny-blanco@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3821435" class="wp-caption-text">赛琳娜·戈麦斯（Selena Gomez）和本尼·布兰科（Benny Blanco）。图片来源：艾米·苏斯曼/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>新音乐跟随戈麦斯向其他演员saoirse Ronan承认，尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-thinks-shes-a-little-too-old-for-the-pop-star-life-3821419">她认为自己“对流行星生活有点老”</a> ，但她将“在我的生活中总是有音乐，因为我的伴侣是一名音乐家，我喜欢有片刻为了娱乐而做。”</p><p>在此之前，她说她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-doubles-down-that-her-music-career-isnt-going-away-3814576">音乐事业“没有消失”</a> ，但是她想专注于表演，因为她坚持自己的“理智”，因为表演可以让她讲述别人的故事而不是比她自己的音乐。</p><p>此前，她与<em>NME</em>的Alex Flood交谈，与ZoeSaldaña一起推广了她的最新电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/emilia-perez"><em>Emilia Perez</em></a> ，她被要求在2020年回到她的上一张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/selena-gomez-rare-the-quietly-confident-star-wrestles-back-her-own-narrative-2595207">Rare</a> 》中有关新音乐的最新消息。当被问及一张新专辑时，戈麦斯回答：“好吧，如果我有一个，我很想谈论它。我认为现在，专注于运动场的这一边真是太好了。我们看，你永远不会知道。” - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/selena-gomez-kurt-cobain-nirvana-zoe-saldana-emilia-perez-3812058">在这里阅读<em>NME</em>与Gomez和Saldaña的完整聊天</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="赛琳娜·戈麦斯（Selena Gomez" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ILZ5wBeSXeE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>索菲亚·布彻（Sophia Butcher）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/emilia-perez-review-zoe-saldana-selena-gomez-flawed-musical-melodrama-3805570">对<em>艾米莉亚·佩雷斯（Emilia Perez）</em>的三星级评论</a>中为<em>NME</em>写道：“您可能从未看过像<i>Emilia Perez</i>这样的电影 - 尽管表演中有足够的肉使您有些高兴，但您<i>可能</i>没有想再次。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2025-nominations-full-list-3831350"><em>艾米利亚·佩雷斯（EmiliaPérez）</em>为今年的奥斯卡颁奖典礼获得了创纪录的13项提名</a>，其中包括最佳电影，萨尔达尼亚（Saldaña）的最佳女演员以及卡拉·索菲亚·加斯科（KarlaSofíaGascón）的最佳女演员，卡拉·索菲亚·加斯科（KarlaSofíaGascón）是第一个被提名为该类别的公开跨性别者。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-and-gracie-abrams-are-teasing-a-collaboration-3839249">塞莱娜·戈麦斯（Selena Gomez）和格雷西·艾布拉姆斯（Gracie Abrams）的职位</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Pendulum的Ben Verse分享了医院约200天的健康更新https://www.nme.com/news/music/pendulums-ben-verse-shares-health-update-about-200-days-in-hospital-3839238?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pendulums-ben-verse-共享健康的日期-About-about-200-Day-Days-in HospitalSurej Singh Wed, 19 Feb 2025 04:21:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsDanceElectronicMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3839238 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Drum N&#39;Bass乐队的前司仪去年被诊断出患有急性单细胞白血病</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pendulums-ben-verse-shares-health-update-about-200-days-in-hospital-3839238">Pendulum的Ben Verse分享了医院约200天的健康更新，</a>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>的首次出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ben-mount-pendulum@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本·“诗歌”山（Ben&#39;The Verse&#39;Mount）在住院超过200天后分享了健康更新 - 请参阅他在下面必须说的话。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pendulum-interview-napalm-new-album-bring-me-the-horizon-reading-leeds-3785482">摆钟谈论狂野的新单曲“ Napalm”，这是一个带给我地平线的“灵感圈”，然后重返雷迪斯</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-former-pendulum-member-ben-verse-after-cancer-diagnosis-3825667">筹款活动开始减轻他的治疗的经济负担</a>之后，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pendulum">摆</a>司令最近的癌症诊断被揭露。芒特在四个月前被诊断出患有急性单细胞白血病。</p><p>在此期间，芒特连续200多天住院。在<a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/j49ca-bens-road-to-recovery" target="_blank" rel="noopener">筹款页面</a>中，山的兄弟杰里米（Mount）的杰里米（Jeremy）分享说，本（Ben）于去年八月首次住院，并怀疑患有结核病。后来发现这是一种“快速增长的抗生素蒸发/抗性”超级咬伤，它在他的肺中产生了脓肿。 </p><figure id="attachment_3825673" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825673" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825673" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Ben-Verse@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Ben-Verse@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Ben-Verse@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Ben-Verse@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Ben-Verse@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Ben-Verse@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Ben-Verse@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825673" class="wp-caption-text"> Ben“ The Verse” Mount与Pendulum Live一起表演。学分：蒂姆·莫森费尔德/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>他再次被送进医院，并在诱发昏迷中呆了六个星期，有时他是否会生存令人怀疑。</p><p>本周早些时候（2月17日），本·芒特（Ben Mount）上Instagram分享了他的健康和住院更新。山躺在床上时透露：“他们终于在208天后让我离开医院。我感到很殴打，但是回家真是太好了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGJN2KBOI-h/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1