ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Swan_Gallet_Euan_Cherry_Joseph_Okpako-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Swan_Gallet_Euan_Cherry_Joseph_Okpako-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Swan_Gallet_Euan_Cherry_Joseph_Okpako-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bashy">Bashy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ayra-starr">Ayra Starr</a>是2025年MOBO奖的最大赢家 - 请参阅下面的获奖者的完整列表。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="953" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/odeal-interview-lustropolis-radar-3822796"><b>探古：LVRN支持的后起之秀与他的AltéFusion重新定义了R＆B</b></a></li></ul><p>庆祝黑人音乐的第27届年度颁奖典礼于周二晚（2月18日）在纽卡斯尔的Utilita竞技场举行，由喜剧演员Eddie Kadi和<i>Love Island</i> Star Indiyah Polack主持。</p><p>该节目于当晚晚上8点在YouTube上直播，而在周五晚上（2月21日）晚上11:25，将在BBC One上进行独家的“所有区域”广播。</p><p>巴西（Bashy）获得了15年来的第一张唱片，“贫穷的是昂贵”的年度最佳专辑奖，<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">这也被<i>NME</i>评为2024年的50张最佳专辑之一</a>。他还被评为最佳嘻哈表演。 </p><figure id="attachment_3774115" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774115" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774115" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bashy-Dennis-Morris.jpg" alt="Bashy。图片来源：丹尼斯·莫里斯（Dennis Morris）。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bashy-Dennis-Morris.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bashy-Dennis-Morris-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bashy-Dennis-Morris-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bashy-Dennis-Morris-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bashy-Dennis-Morris-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bashy-Dennis-Morris-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774115" class="wp-caption-text"> Bashy。图片来源：丹尼斯·莫里斯（Dennis Morris）。</figcaption></figure><p>其他多个获奖者是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/darkoo">Darkoo</a> ，他们赢得了Diss Dior的最佳女性表演以及“最喜欢的女孩”的年度最佳歌曲和Ayra Starr，他们为最佳非洲音乐表演和最佳国际表演挑选了锣。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/odeal">奥德尔（Odeal）</a>是另一个带回家的艺术家 - 最佳新人和最佳R＆B/Soul Act。</p><p> Elsewhere, Central Cee took home Best Male Act for a record third time, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a> won Best Jazz Act and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alt-blk-era">ALT BLK ERA</a> were named Best Alternative Music Act.</p><h2> <b>See the full list of winners here:</b></h2><p> <b>Best Male Act:</b> Central Cee<br /> <b>Best Female Act:</b> Darkoo<br /> <b>Best Newcomer:</b> Odeal<br /> <b>Album Of The Year:</b> Bashy – &#39;Being Poor Is Expensive&#39;<br /> <b>Song Of The Year:</b> Darkoo (ft. Dess Dior) – &#39;Favourite Girl&#39;<br /> <b>Video Of The Year:</b> Mnelia – &#39;My Man&#39;<br /> <b>Best Hip Hop Act:</b> Bashy<br /> <b>Best Grime Act:</b> Scorcher<br /> <b>Best Drill Act:</b> Pozer<br /> <b>Best R&amp;B/Soul Act:</b> Odeal<br /> <b>Best Media Personality:</b> 90s Baby Show<br /> <b>Best African Music Act:</b> Ayra Starr<br /> <b>Best Performance In A TV Show/Film:</b> Jacob Anderson in <i>Interview With The Vampire</i><br /> <b>Best Electronic/Dance Music Act:</b> TSHA<br /> <b>Best Gospel Act:</b> Annatoria<br /> <b>Best Jazz Act:</b> Ezra Collective<br /> <b>Best Producer:</b> Juls<br /> <b>Best Caribbean Music Act:</b> Shenseea<br /> <b>Best Alternative Music Act:</b> ALT BLK ERA<br /> <b>Best International Act:</b> Ayra Starr </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Darkoo ft Dess Dior -  Favourite Girl (Official video)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xSaBe60hBLU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> In addition, two special awards were handed out at the ceremony: Olympic gold medal-winning heptathlete Denise Lewis won the MOBO Paving The Way Award, while dancehall legend <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vybz-kartel">Vybz Kartel</a> won the MOBO Impact Award.</p><p> The show also included a number of live performances, from the likes of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/krept-and-konan">Krept &amp; Konan</a> , Spice, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nova-twins">Nova Twins</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nao">Nao</a> , as well as winners Bashy, Darkoo and Odeal.</p><p> Ahead of the ceremony, MOBO founder and CEO Kanya King CBE said: “MOBO has always been about shaping cultural moments that celebrate the richness and diversity of music, and this year will be no exception. Our R&amp;B celebration promises to be a defining highlight, alongside an incredible showcase of genres on the MOBO stage.</p><p> “There&#39;s something truly special about bringing these moments to life—experiences that fans can only witness at the MOBO Awards. We can&#39;t wait to unveil even more surprises as we build up to February 18.”</p><p> The post<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-mobo-awards-2025-3839156">Here are all the winners from the MOBO Awards 2025</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
